      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/former-jetblue-ceo-hayes-lead-airbus-north-america-2024-04-22/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲飞机制造商周一表示，捷蓝航空前首席执行官罗宾·海耶斯已被任命为空客北美业务的新负责人。]]></description>
