      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/shale-oil-gains-slow-deepwater-port-struggles-customers-2024-04-22/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着美国页岩油在过去十年的蓬勃发展，一家石油管道公司雄心勃勃地在德克萨斯州海岸投资数十亿美元的出口港口，将国内原油运送到欧洲和亚洲的买家。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/shale-oil-gains-slow-deepwater-port-struggles-customers-2024-04-22/</guid>
